      "body@en": "<p>Hello colleague,</p><p>ECAT opened in April 2023 in Sevilla, Spain. It should grow to 30 people by 2024. They shall support European regulators in their investigations of automated systems.</p><p>AlgorithmWatch wrote an explainer about it: <a href='https://algorithmwatch.org/en/dsa-explained/'>https://algorithmwatch.org/en/dsa-explained/</a>.</p><p>Cheers,</p><p>Lisbet</p>"
